BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:FnMd5W4pjDh8ODa_wRNej
SUMMARY:PCC Cooking Class - Date Night: Northwest Feast
DTSTAMP:20260325T061937Z
DTSTART:20260404T010000Z
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the flavors of our region alongside a partner in this
	 date night cooking class. With our experts as your guide\, you’ll learn t
	o oven-roast king salmon so it’s perfectly flaky\, and practice carefully 
	reducing a cream sauce. For a side\, you’ll try your hand at a multi-step 
	process for turning out smashed potatoes with crispy golden edges. And for
	 dessert\, you’ll learn to gently heat ingredients for a panna cotta witho
	ut scalding. You’ll leave class ready to recreate this Northwest-inspired 
	menu at home. \n\nContains seafood and dairy. \n\nAbout the instructor: Ou
	r seasoned instructors and chefs have been chosen to be a part of PCC Cook
	s because of their culinary expertise and sincere enthusiasm and talent fo
	r teaching. \n\nThis is a hands-on format class for adults. \n\nThis cooki
	ng class is available at multiple PCC locations and dates. See below for d
	etails: \n\nBellevue PCC \n\n-Friday\, April 3\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\n-Satur
	day\, April 4\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\n-Friday\, May 1\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm  \n\nB
	othell PCC \n\n-Friday\, April 3\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\n-Friday\, May 1\, 6:
	00 - 8:00 pm  \n\nBurien PCC \n\n-Friday\, April 3\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\n-F
	riday\, May 1\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\nColumbia City PCC \n\n-Friday\, April 3
	\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\n-Saturday\, April 4\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\nEdmonds PCC
	 \n\n-Friday\, April 3\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\n-Friday\, May 1\, 6:00 - 8:00 
	pm  \n\nGreen Lake Village PCC \n\n-Friday\, April 3\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\n
	-Saturday\, April 4\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm \n\n-Saturday\, April 25\, 6:00 - 8:0
	0 pm \n\n-Friday\, May 1\, 6:00 - 8:00 pm\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/
	events/#/details/pcc-cooking-class-date-night-northwest-feast/18296339/202
	6-04-03T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drink
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/pcc-cooking-class-date-ni
	ght-northwest-feast/18296339/2026-04-03T00
LOCATION:Edmonds PCC\, 9803 Edmonds Way\, Edmonds\, WA
